input_str: If your car is stolen in Houston, chances are the crime is ever solved are very low. That's according to newly released Houston Police Department crime clearance rates.In fact, auto theft is the least-solved crime by HPD. The department released data going back to 2009.Burglary is just as bad, as Margaret Galvan knows first-hand."I would at least give it 3 to 4 months at the most, but nothing," Galvan, a single mother of 4,
